@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ytpjkl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v2
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.03 - v1 + 0.88)) - wp.sin((v0 + 0.90 - v2 + 0.89)))
    v0 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.94 - v2 + 0.36)) * v2)
    tmp = (0.65 + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.53) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.23)))
    data[tid] = v0
